title: Did The quiz, didn't get the icon
body:
The star guardian quiz, hit redeem icon (or whatever the button was) i haven't recieved the icon, do i need a star guardian skin on my account to redeem?

BTW well done on the skins, super impressed all are so good, but im poor so i can't buy any of them :)

replies.body: You probably didn't notice this but it actually states to allow for up to one week after you claim the icon. Just thought I'd mention this.
I haven't got mine yet also, but as usual it takes them a while to send these things out, so have patience)
I did the quiz last week, no icon yet...
Oh lmao, i don't read XD, i just do
